{"tid":840971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日被港鐵捉我用特優飛，我兇鳩職員大鬧港鐵","createTime":"2018-09-29T08:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T16:03:47.000Z","uid":38539,"like":8,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74661e5cd8c57ff8338cc1c02476e9293a9141ad","tid":840971,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"幾個職員夾我入房，填完張form叫我交五佰蚊，我問佢知唔知我係邊個，佢話唔識，我指住張form姓名嗰欄，佢諗咗陣「哦，宇生，麻煩俾錢」，我見佢係斯文人，打算用對話解決，於是放低五舊水喺枱面，氣定神閒同佢講「錢係枱上，命係身上，你覺得邊樣份量重啲，就拎去啦！」，佢零思考就伸手攞走啲錢，真係被啲職員吹鳩脹..."},{"pid":"46d305c0df56acb15e26868baaa179bcb6183435","tid":840971,"uid":199590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:19:51.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"cb5d47e37acc2c3244086694c74062ddd54337c5","tid":840971,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"留你一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n#respectmtr"},{"pid":"b63b5c25bf6ead9ccfbf19b9efa459697bbff98a","tid":840971,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ff6e3a9be8e170b8694521baa46f16147e8c9d3","tid":840971,"uid":203036,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"玩時玩，千奇唔好攞港鐵兩個字黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81a3dec1d7ea59ca3f874ad1ef2af93e085eea9","tid":840971,"uid":202409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/171336_c3575084fcd97f01a9f6933b8297f0be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F171336_c3575084fcd97f01a9f6933b8297f0be.jpg&h=084c1a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇是咁，重作la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd1c4d35f7dfbfb4e89bf7b9782f96b8a3a7f8e","tid":840971,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislik